&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GuZhengSVT/Hugo-media/2024/12/1795319606.jpeg" alt="IMG_0434.jpeg">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>因为春天来过</title><link>https://guzhengsvt.github.io/zh-cn/post/poetry/%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%9D%A5%E8%BF%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 16:52:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://guzhengsvt.github.io/zh-cn/post/poetry/%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%9D%A5%E8%BF%87/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="谨以此诗献给我生命中那颗polaris">
