　　&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>中秋，给家人打个电话吧</title><link>https://guzhengsvt.github.io/zh-cn/post/thoughts/%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E7%BB%99%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D%E5%90%A7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 16:41:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://guzhengsvt.github.io/zh-cn/post/thoughts/%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E7%BB%99%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D%E5%90%A7/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
